Management's discussion and analysis, or MD&A, of our results of operations and financial condition is provided as a supplement to the audited annual consolidated financial statements and unaudited interim consolidated financial statements and notes thereto included elsewhere herein to help provide an understanding of our financial condition, changes in financial condition and results of our operations. The information included in MD&A should be read in conjunction with the annual and interim consolidated financial
