Messrs. Carroll, Sullivan and Gallagher were not executive officers of Cablevision in 2010. As employees of RMH, their base salaries were reviewed by the Company's executive management, working within guidelines and established by Cablevision's compensation committee. The base salaries of Messrs. Carroll and Gallagher were increased from $900,000 to $950,000 and from $420,000 to $436,800, respectively, in 2010 from 2009. Mr. Sullivan joined RMH in mid-2010, and his base salary was established at $575,000 at that time.
 
