in 2010 depended on achievement of performance objectives at each of our national programming networks. The payout to Mr. Carroll in 2010 was based on a weighted-average achievement of all relevant business units of 113.63%, and then modified slightly to reflect individual performance ratings. In the case of Mr. Dolan, payouts under the annual incentive program in 2010 depended on achievement of performance objectives at all business units at Cablevision. The payout to Mr. Dolan in 2010 was based on a weighted-average achievement of all Cablevision business units of 147.3%. Mr. Dolan's annual incentive is not adjusted for individual performance.
